law.history: Repealed 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 182, sec. 26, effective July 15, 1986. -- Amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 141, sec. 98, effective July 1, 1982. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 16, sec. 1. --Created 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 202, sec. 1.

metadata.note: 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 396, sec. 107 would have amended this section effective July 1, 1982. However, 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 396 was repealed by 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 141, sec. 146, also effective July 1, 1982.
